title: When can we expect Leland to get a gym such as Gold\'s or another well-known chain?
text:
We're sorry but we're unable to answer your question. These are the
known businesses coming to Leland. http://www.myreporter.com/?p=2619

As for a gym, if one decides to come here, we'll publish it online
and in the StarNews paper. But as of now we don't know of any.
